event.title: Open Source Founders Summit
event.metaDesc: Learn from peers building open source companies
event.content: May 19-20 in Paris, France. Open source companies face challenges and opportunities that proprietary software companies never encounter. General startup programs, investors and your own employees often wonâ€™t understand how to navigate these challenges or take advantage of the opportunities unless they have open source experience. Open Source Founders Summit gives founders a place to learn from each other and support each other in building open source companies.
